## ğŸ›  Step-by-Step Implementation

### Step 1: Create AI Agent Service (Backend)

Create: `backend/services/aiAgentService.js`

This service contains the core AI decision-making logic with different difficulty levels.

### Step 2: Create AI Agent Controller (Backend)

Create: `backend/controllers/aiAgentController.js`

This controller handles API requests for AI decisions and actions.

### Step 3: Add AI Routes (Backend)

Create: `backend/routes/aiAgentRoutes.js`

Add routes to your Express server.

### Step 4: Create Enhanced AI Hook (Frontend)

Create: `frontend/hooks/useEnhancedAI.ts`

This hook connects to your backend AI service.

### Step 5: Integrate into Board Component

Update: `frontend/components/game/ai-board/ai-board.tsx`

